title: Hafiz Ur Rehman Khan Dareshak wins NA-188 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz Candidate Hafiz Ur Rehman Khan Dareshak has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-188 Rajanpur-II by securing 85,936 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate Sardar Ahmed Ali Khan Dareshak, who bagged 70,206 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 50.5 percent.
